Wang Ting

Attorney-at- Law

DeBund Law Offices & Bridge IP Law Commentary

Wang Ting, an attorney-at-law, specializes in intellectual property and corporate issues. She studied laws in Tongji University and obtained her LLM degree.

Tel: 021-52134900 Fax: 021-52134911

Email: wangting@debund.com

【Qualifications】

Wang passed her bar examination in 2012 and has been practicing law since 2015;

【Practice Areas】

Wang practices primarily within the trademark, copyright and other intellectual properties laws, anti-unfair competition law, corporation law, contract laws.

Wang is skilled at intellectual property dispute resolution, IPR management services, trademark registration, opposition, review, license, transfer and protections; drafting and reviewing IP related contracts, such as technology transfer license, game IP license, IP license agreement, user agreement; providing services for other IP investment and financing;

Wang has been legal consultant of many well-known enterprises, and provides professional legal opinions for IP protection, daily operation and dispute resolution.

【Working Experiences】

Shanghai Debund Law Offices

【Education】

Tongji University, Law, LLM

【Working Language】

Chinese and English

